A Last Call Hospitality Brand

Enjoy live music, tropical drinks, and tasty food at The Bungalow Bar & 
Grill in Boynton Beach, your local escape to relaxing, flavorful 
experiences.

Host Your Event Under the Palms
Planning a birthday bash, engagement party, corporate happy hour, or just a night out with your crew? The Bungalow at Boynton Beach offers a private event space that blends tropical charm with laid-back luxury. Whether you're hosting 20 or 200 guests, our team will help you craft a custom experience — complete with bold cocktails, vibrant bites, and the Key West vibes we’re known for.
Fill out the form below to get the party started. We'll be in touch soon to bring your vision to life.
